    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/2f5a251abe2d12c189379f9dee586d65.avif?t=1771857151\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/9a9d9764611aa0a9c5cfc4ff50be1807.poster.avif?t=1771857151\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/9a9d9764611aa0a9c5cfc4ff50be1807.webm?t=1771857151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/9a9d9764611aa0a9c5cfc4ff50be1807.mp4?t=1771857151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一名观察者，正在远程监视闭路电视系统中是否存在可疑活动。无论你监视的地方看起来多么平凡，它们都是超自然现象的发生地。你的工作不仅仅是观察而已，还要识别发生的异常并采取适当的对策。请注意：无论是什么潜伏在那里，最终都会注意到它正在被注视——而当它开始回望时，可能已经太晚了……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/d88c69a5acf14b05b233dd4d8e3cab0c.avif?t=1771857151\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/3660718635fe40f255c0e47b8d444658.poster.avif?t=1771857151\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/3660718635fe40f255c0e47b8d444658.webm?t=1771857151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/3660718635fe40f255c0e47b8d444658.mp4?t=1771857151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spectator的故事背景设定在令人感到惶恐的日常场所，从Slender和Backrooms等故事中汲取灵感，进入让人毛骨悚然的恐怖小说世界，创造出令人深感不安的阴森体验，当你以为安全时，故事内容却不断出现反转。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可观察和监控六种不同的环境。每个关卡可以出现超过六十种不同的异常现象，这些异象是通过程序生成的，以保证不可预测性。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/0379d2903c3d1eacc640ced2ed120f3c.poster.avif?t=1771857151\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/0379d2903c3d1eacc640ced2ed120f3c.webm?t=1771857151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/0379d2903c3d1eacc640ced2ed120f3c.mp4?t=1771857151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏都有独特的挑战性和恐怖感。如果在凌晨 6 点之前错过太多异常现象，无论发生什么，你都会遭遇不测。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spectator 支持超宽屏分辨率、触摸屏和开箱即用的控制器，并具有逼真的视觉风格以优化体验。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/ba29465906e04792ca081d063ad2291d.poster.avif?t=1771857151\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/ba29465906e04792ca081d063ad2291d.webm?t=1771857151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132450/extras/ba29465906e04792ca081d063ad2291d.mp4?t=1771857151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >社区翻译已融入游戏，让 Spectator 支持超过 29 种语言！</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 俄语, 日语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 意大利语, 阿拉伯语, 保加利亚语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 匈牙利语, 越南语, 希腊语, 丹麦语, 韩语, 荷兰语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 泰语, 土耳其语, 芬兰语, 捷克语, 瑞典语, 繁体中文, 乌克兰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
